  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Gallery Card Image Error State Positioning\n\nUpdate the CSS for the image error state in gallery card images to use `position: initial` instead of the current positioning value.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the `.image-error` class within the `.gallery-card-image` component\n- Change the position property from its current value to `position: initial`\n- Verify the error state displays correctly when images fail to load\n- Ensure the change doesn't break the layout of other gallery card elements\n- Test across different viewport sizes to confirm responsive behavior remains intact\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Error state appearance when gallery is in grid vs list view\n- Interaction with any overlay or placeholder elements\n- Proper alignment with card borders and padding",
